w.operate-first.cloud/\">https://www.operate-first.cloud/</a> ?</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Menu (item goes to landing page)</p>\n<ul class=\"pf-c-list\">\n<li>\n<p>Doing things (Who are you)</p>\n<ul class=\"pf-c-list\">\n<li>Learners</li>\n<li>Data science users</li>\n<li>SRE (GitOps) users</li>\n<li>Open source dev users</li>\n<li>Op1st cloud operators</li>\n<li>User support</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Docs &#x26; Training (What do you want to learn)</p>\n<ul class=\"pf-c-list\">\n<li>Community Handbook</li>\n<li>Training</li>\n<li>Cloud operations documentation</li>\n<li>Help/FAQ</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>About Op1st (Who are we)</p>\n<ul class=\"pf-c-list\">\n<li>“Mission” (Read more)</li>\n<li>Open community cloud environment</li>\n<li>Community of practice</li>\n<li>Getting involved</li>\n<li>Glossary (link to page)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zt2IEUz.png\">\n(Menu mock-up)</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"actions\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#actions\" aria-label=\"actions permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Actions:</h2>\n<ul class=\"pf-c-list\">\n<li>putting ideas into <a href=\"https://github.com/operate-first/community/issues/40\">https://github.com/operate-first/community/issues/40</a></li>\n</ul>","fields":{"srcLink":"https://github.com/operate-first/community/blob/master/sig-community/wg-website-updates/meeting-notes/20220322-meeting-notes.md"},"frontmatter":{"title":"","de